From David Ray Subject Re Hallusion info Sean Murphy wrote Has anyone seen hallusions You can buy a poster of them and it looks like a simple dot pattern when you first look at it but if you focus behind it you see a I'm looking for a program that generates these There's a company in Texas that makes them but I doubt if they're giving the program Any help would be There is a program included with the book Virtual Reality Playhouse which will let you generate these It's not a very powerful program but it does an acceptable job for experimentation